{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"敬畏的人們必有一種收獲，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"許多園圃和葡萄，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"和兩乳圓潤，年齡劃一的少女，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"和滿杯的醴泉。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"他們在那裡面聽不到惡言和謊話。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"那是從你的主發出的報酬——充足的賞賜。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"他是天地萬物的主，是至仁的主，他們不敢向他陳說。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"在精神和眾天神排班肅立之日，他們不得說話，唯至仁主所特許而且能說正話的，才敢發言。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"那是必有的日子，誰意欲，誰就擇取一個向他的主的歸宿。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"我的確警告你們一種臨近的刑罰，在那日，各人將要看見自己所已做的工作，不信道的人們將要說：「啊！但願我原是塵土。」"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"誓以急掣的，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"輕曳的，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"奔馳的，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"先驅的，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"決策的，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"當震動者震動，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"而續髮者續髮之日，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"在那日，許多心將忐忑不安，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"許多眼將不敢仰視。"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"他們說：「我們必定復元嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"那是在我們已變成朽骨的時候嗎？」"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"他們說：「然則，那是一次虧折的復原。」"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"那只是一次吼聲，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"他們忽然在地面之上。"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"穆薩的故事已來臨你了嗎？"}]}